{
  "info": {
    "name": "Knowledge Platform - Stage 1 API Tests",
    "description": "# 知识库与内容发布平台 - 阶段1测试接口文档\n\n## 环境变量说明\n| 变量 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| `baseUrl` | `http://localhost:8080` | 网关地址 |\n| `token` | (自动填充) | 用户JWT令牌 |\n| `userId` | (自动填充) | 当前用户ID |\n| `role` | (自动填充) | 当前用户角色 |\n| `articleId` | (自动填充) | 测试文章ID |\n\n## 测试流程\n1. **注册用户** → 普通用户注册\n2. **注册管理员** → 管理员账号注册\n3. **登录(用户)** → 获取普通用户token\n4. **登录(管理员)** → 获取管理员token\n5. **创建文章** → 草稿创建\n6. **发布文章** → 发布并触发RabbitMQ广播\n7. **修改文章** → 仅作者/管理员可修改\n8. **文章列表** → 分页查询已发布文章\n9. **文章详情** → 查看详情并触发热度+1\n10. **评论文章** → 异步写入评论\n11. **点赞文章** → 防重点赞\n12. **热搜榜单** → 查看Top 10\n13. **越权测试** → 验证权限控制\n14. **注销** → Token加入黑名单\n\n## 快速开始\n导入后，先执行文件夹 `1-用户服务` 中的注册和登录，token 会自动存入环境变量，后续请求自动携带。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "knowledge-platform-stage1"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1-用户服务 (User Service)",
      "description": "注册、登录、注销 - JWT认证流程",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "注册普通用户",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('用户注册成功:', json.data);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('normalUsername', 'testuser');",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "// 测试用例验证",
                  "pm.test('状态码 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('返回Result格式', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(200);",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('id');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('username');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('role', 'user');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"testuser\",\n    \"password\": \"test123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "register"]
            },
            "description": "注册一个普通用户（角色默认为 user）\n\n### 验证点\n- 返回 200 及用户信息\n- role 字段为 user\n- 重复注册应返回错误"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "注册管理员",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    console.log('管理员注册成功:', pm.response.json().data);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('adminUsername', 'admin');",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('状态码 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('角色为admin', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.role).to.eql('admin');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"admin\",\n    \"password\": \"admin123456\",\n    \"role\": \"admin\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "register"]
            },
            "description": "注册管理员账号\n\n### 验证点\n- role 字段为 admin"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "注册-重复用户名(异常测试)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('状态码 400', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(400); });",
                  "pm.test('返回用户名已存在错误', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.message).to.include('已存在');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"testuser\",\n    \"password\": \"another123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "register"]
            },
            "description": "使用已存在的用户名注册，验证唯一性校验"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "注册-缺少参数(异常测试)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('状态码 400', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(400); });",
                  "pm.test('返回参数校验失败', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(400);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"\",\n    \"password\": \"\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "register"]
            },
            "description": "提交空用户名和密码，验证参数校验"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "登录(普通用户)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    // 自动保存token到环境变量",
                  "    pm.environment.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userId', json.data.userId);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('role', json.data.role);",
                  "    console.log('Token已保存:', json.data.token.substring(0, 30) + '...');",
                  "    console.log('UserId:', json.data.userId);",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('状态码 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('返回token', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('token');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('tokenType', 'Bearer');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('userId');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('role', 'user');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"testuser\",\n    \"password\": \"test123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "login"]
            },
            "description": "普通用户登录，获取JWT Token\n\n### 自动处理\n- token 自动存入环境变量\n- userId、role 自动存入环境变量\n- 后续请求自动携带 Authorization 头"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "登录(管理员)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('adminToken', json.data.token);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('adminUserId', json.data.userId);",
                  "    console.log('Admin Token已保存');",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('状态码 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('角色为admin', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().data.role).to.eql('admin');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"admin\",\n    \"password\": \"admin123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "login"]
            },
            "description": "管理员登录，获取admin JWT Token"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "登录-错误密码(异常测试)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('状态码 401', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(401); });",
                  "pm.test('返回用户名或密码错误', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.message).to.include('错误');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"testuser\",\n    \"password\": \"wrongpassword\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "login"]
            },
            "description": "使用错误密码登录，验证认证失败"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "注销",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('状态码 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('注销成功', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/logout",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "注销当前Token，加入Redis黑名单\n\n### 验证点\n- 注销后Token不可再用（需先执行登录后再测注销后访问）"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2-文章服务 (Article Service)",
      "description": "文章的创建、发布、修改、删除、列表、详情和热搜榜单",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "创建文章(草稿)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('articleId', json.data.id);",
                  "    console.log('文章创建成功, ID:', json.data.id);",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('状态码 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('文章状态为DRAFT', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('id');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.status).to.eql('DRAFT');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('title');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('content');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.authorId).to.eql(pm.environment.get('userId'));",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"title\": \"Spring Cloud微服务最佳实践\",\n    \"content\": \"本文详细介绍了Spring Cloud微服务架构的核心组件，包括服务注册与发现、配置中心、API网关、负载均衡、熔断降级等内容。通过实际案例演示了如何使用Nacos、Sentinel、Gateway等组件构建高可用的微服务体系。\\n\\n## 核心要点\\n1. 服务注册与发现：Nacos\\n2. API网关：Spring Cloud Gateway\\n3. 流量控制：Sentinel\\n4. 配置管理：Nacos Config\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles"]
            },
            "description": "创建一篇文章，默认状态为草稿(DRAFT)\n\n### 自动处理\n- articleId 自动存入环境变量\n\n### 验证点\n- status 为 DRAFT\n- authorId 等于当前用户ID"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "创建文章2(草稿)-用于列表测试",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('articleId2', pm.response.json().data.id);",
                  "    console.log('文章2创建成功, ID:', pm.response.json().data.id);",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('状态码 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('文章2状态为DRAFT', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().data.status).to.eql('DRAFT');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"title\": \"Redis高并发场景应用指南\",\n    \"content\": \"Redis作为高性能的键值存储系统，在高并发场景下有着广泛的应用。本文探讨了Redis在缓存穿透、缓存击穿、缓存雪崩等问题上的解决方案，以及如何使用Redis实现分布式锁、排行榜、消息队列等功能。\\n\\n## 应用场景\\n1. 热点数据缓存\\n2. 实时排行榜(ZSET)\\n3. 消息队列(Stream)\\n4. 分布式锁\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles"]
            },
            "description": "创建第二篇文章用于列表和热度排序测试"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "创建文章-未登录(异常测试)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('状态码 401', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(401); });",
                  "pm.test('返回未授权错误', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(401);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"title\": \"未登录创建文章\",\n    \"content\": \"这篇文章不应该被创建成功\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles"]
            },
            "description": "不带Authorization头创建文章，验证网关鉴权拦截"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "发布文章",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('状态码 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('文章状态变为PUBLISHED', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.status).to.eql('PUBLISHED');",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('发布触发RabbitMQ消息(查看服务日志确认)', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().code).to.eql(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}/publish",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles", "{{articleId}}", "publish"]
            },
            "description": "将文章从草稿状态发布，触发RabbitMQ异步广播\n\n### 验证点\n- status 变为 PUBLISHED\n- RabbitMQ消息已发送（查看article-service日志）"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "发布文章2",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('状态码 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId2}}/publish",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles", "{{articleId2}}", "publish"]
            },
            "description": "发布第二篇文章"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "修改文章",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('状态码 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('标题已更新', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.title).to.include('(修订版)');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"title\": \"Spring Cloud微服务最佳实践(修订版)\",\n    \"content\": \"【更新】本文详细介绍了Spring Cloud微服务架构的核心组件...\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{articleId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles", "{{articleId}}"]
            },
            "description": "修改文章标题和内容，仅作者或管理员可操作\n\n### 验证点\n- 文章标题更新成功"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "文章列表(分页)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('状态码 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('返回已发布文章列表', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(200);",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.be.an('array');",
                  "    if (json.data.length > 0) {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data[0]).to.have.property('id');",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data[0]).to.have.property('title');",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data[0]).to.have.property('likeCount');",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data[0]).not.to.have.property('content');",
                  "    }",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles?page=1&size=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "page", "value": "1"},
                {"key": "size", "value": "20"}
              ]
            },
            "description": "分页查询最新文章列表\n\n### 验证点\n- 只返回已发布(PUBLISHED)状态文章\n- 列表项不含content字段\n- 按创建时间倒序排列\n- 草稿文章不出现在列表中"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "文章详情(触发热度)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
